person.persName: Daniel S. Collins (Webster county, kentucky, farmer )

body.p: Webster County, Kentucky, farmer. Kentucky native. Married to Letty Ann Collins. Father of Jeff D. Collins and L. B. Collins. Farmer in Webster County, Kentucky, in 1860.
